message.raw:
Updated install script
Fixed pointer dereference bug that could cause segfault in genomedata-load-data
Added extra track reference line to test datafile
Made "ignoring data" output of genomedata-load-data less frequent for wigfix
  files and only be printed in verbose mode (for all files)
